hesitates now that you mention it i recall that a note was handed to her as we left the church she read it turned pale and crushed it into her glove i thought it a trifle perhaps some girlish congratulation that my lord may prove the most important fact of all

00:08:57,980 --> 00:09:02,720
Holmes leaned back, his eyes half closed, as though assembling the various threads in his mind,

00:09:02,720 --> 00:09:07,100
I for my part, was already marvelling at the possibilities which the case suggested.

00:09:07,100 --> 00:09:09,930
Thus began the strange adventure of the noble bachelor,

00:09:09,930 --> 00:09:14,509
one of the most singular episodes it has ever been my fortune to share with Sherlock Holmes.

00:09:14,509 --> 00:09:16,210
Hmm, Lord St. Hmm.

00:09:16,210 --> 00:09:21,990
Simon sat erect upon the settee, the faintest suggestion of irritation upon his refined features,

00:09:21,990 --> 00:09:26,070
as though his very dignity chafed against the necessity of explanation.

00:09:26,070 --> 00:09:28,950
Holmes, however, remained perfectly at ease,

00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:30,840
his long fingers steeply together,

00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:34,320
his gaze fixed with quiet intensity upon our client.

00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:38,700
You mention, my lord, that a note was delivered to your bride

00:09:38,700 --> 00:09:40,910
at the very door of the church.

00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:44,129
Do you recall by whom it was handed to her?

00:09:44,129 --> 00:09:45,940
A small page boy, I believe,

00:09:45,940 --> 00:09:47,840
a messenger from one of the attendants, perhaps.

00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,620
I paid little attention, being myself occupied

00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,590
with the congratulations of my friends.

00:09:51,590 --> 00:09:54,320
And the note itself, you did not see it?

00:09:54,320 --> 00:10:11,960
no sir she read it hastily pale visibly and thrust it into her glove i thought no more of it until her disappearance did she carry the note with her when she left the house in lancaster gate i cannot say if she did it has not been found just howard i go to

00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:17,250
A more curious circumstance, indeed. A sudden letter on the very threshold of matrimony,

00:10:17,250 --> 00:10:20,890
and vanishing thereafter, surely the two events are connected.

00:10:20,890 --> 00:10:29,139
Just so, Watson, we must treat them as contiguous phenomena. Now, my lord, you mentioned that Miss

00:10:29,139 --> 00:10:34,750
Doran was observed later in Hyde Park with a gentleman who was the observer.

00:10:34,750 --> 00:10:38,800
One of the footmen from my father-in-law's household, he stated that he saw a lady

00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:43,349
resembling my wife, in company with a tall man with a moustache, walking beside the serpentine.

00:10:43,349 --> 00:10:51,049
He swears to her identity. Did he hear them speak? No, only that they appeared absorbed in each other,

00:10:51,049 --> 00:10:59,419
walking arm in arm. That is very suggestive. Tell me further, Lord Saint. Simon, did your wife show

00:10:59,419 --> 00:11:07,509
any peculiarities of demeanour on the days preceding the wedding? Any reluctance? Any agitation?

00:11:07,509 --> 00:11:10,140
I cannot deny that she was somewhat restless.

00:11:10,140 --> 00:11:12,380
At the rehearsal she seemed preoccupied.

00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:14,220
At one moment I found her in tears,

00:11:14,220 --> 00:11:17,870
though she quickly explained them as the result of parting from her father's American friends.

00:11:17,870 --> 00:11:23,000
Ah, at this, Mr. Francis Morton, was he one of those friends?

00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:25,950
With a frown, I have heard the name, yes.

00:11:25,950 --> 00:11:28,080
It was said to be an acquaintance of hers in California,

00:11:28,080 --> 00:11:30,029
but I gave the matter no thought.

00:11:30,029 --> 00:11:34,080
