00:11:34,080 --> 00:11:41,230
acquaintances, when overlooked, proved to be the very key to the enigma. At this quiet remark,

00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:46,840
Lord Saint, why't? Simon flushed slightly, but he restrained his irritation, perhaps mindful that

00:11:46,840 --> 00:11:51,450
he had placed himself in Holmes's hands. I'm not here to argue, sir, but to learn the truth,

00:11:51,450 --> 00:11:57,360
if this Mr. Smith, a murtan, has spirited my wife away, then let him be found and punished.

00:11:57,360 --> 00:12:05,039
Unished? My lord, let us not anticipate. It may prove, rather, that some former obligation has

00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:12,379
reasserted itself. You mean another marriage? I hinted nothing. I merely keep the avenues of

00:12:12,379 --> 00:12:19,329
inference open. Combs rose and began pacing the carpet, his dressing gown sweeping behind him,

00:12:19,329 --> 00:12:24,139
his long, humorous, nervous fingers flicking idly at the air as though he plucked threads

00:12:24,139 --> 00:12:25,889
from the unseen room of fate.

00:12:25,889 --> 00:12:28,500
Tell me, Lord St. Simon,

00:12:28,500 --> 00:12:31,819
what of the clothing your bride wore at her disappearance?

00:12:31,819 --> 00:12:32,899
..

00:12:32,899 --> 00:12:35,299
