Hmm.

00:12:55,840 --> 00:12:57,840
Then the facts are thus.

00:12:57,840 --> 00:13:08,840
A bride receives a note at the church, reads it with agitation, conceals it, proceeds to her father's house, then vanishes.

00:13:08,840 --> 00:13:11,840
She is seen with a gentleman in Hyde Park.

00:13:11,840 --> 00:13:15,840
The police are at fort because they lack imagination.

00:13:15,840 --> 00:13:18,840
For myself, the case is transparent.

00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:21,840
Transparent homes? Surely not already.

00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:28,600
My dear Watson, to see is easy when one knows where to look.

00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:32,870
He resumed his seat and fixed Lord St. Simon with a penetrating glance.

00:13:32,870 --> 00:13:39,050
My lord, you will, I trust, excuse a frankness which is necessary.

00:13:39,050 --> 00:13:44,280
You married Miss Hattie Duran for her wealth and she married you for your title.

00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:48,140
There is no shame in acknowledging the truth.

00:13:48,140 --> 00:13:51,779
But she had, it appears, a prior tie.

00:13:51,779 --> 00:13:56,000
A bond of the heart stronger than that of ambition.

00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:59,700
That bond reasserted itself at the very altar.

00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,820
..

00:14:00,820 --> 00:14:03,379
Angrily, you dare insinuate.

00:14:03,379 --> 00:14:05,550
I insinuate nothing.

00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:08,620
I merely read the facts as they lie.

00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:12,650
Whether she has fled to her former lover or has been taken by him,

00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:14,870
the result is the same.

00:14:14,870 --> 00:14:16,720
Your wife is absent.

00:14:16,720 --> 00:14:21,600
Our task is to trace her and to secure her safety.

00:14:21,600 --> 00:14:23,670
And what of my honour, sir?

00:14:23,670 --> 00:14:29,639
Dear, your honour, my lord, must stand upon the truth, not upon illusion.

00:14:29,639 --> 00:14:33,700
For a moment, the young nobleman seemed about to make an indignant retort.

00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:37,980
Then, perceiving perhaps the futility of contention, he rose with dignity.

00:14:37,980 --> 00:14:40,710
