00:15:07,779 --> 00:15:14,379
Consider the note at the church, the agitation, the disappearance, the sighting in the park.

00:15:14,379 --> 00:15:18,379
These form a sequence, too consistent for chance.

00:15:18,379 --> 00:15:19,950
Um, who?

00:15:19,950 --> 00:15:24,069
