00:15:24,069 --> 00:15:26,590
That is precisely what we shall learn.

00:15:26,590 --> 00:15:28,509
But the main principle is clear.

00:15:28,509 --> 00:15:30,759
The lady left willingly.

00:15:30,759 --> 00:15:33,190
