00:16:22,060 --> 00:16:23,759
of self importance it was

00:16:23,759 --> 00:16:25,580
Inspector Lestrade of Scotland Yard

00:16:25,580 --> 00:16:28,180
ha Mr. Holmes good day to you

00:16:28,180 --> 00:16:29,980
