Lestrade

00:16:39,480 --> 00:16:43,230
Smugly, why some rogue she picked up in America, no doubt.

00:16:43,230 --> 00:16:46,000
We shall comb the docks and nab him yet.

00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:48,889
Admirable energy, as always.

00:16:48,889 --> 00:16:54,360
But may I inquire, have you considered the possibility that the lady departed willingly?

00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:55,620
..

00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,519
Willingly? Nonsense.

00:16:57,519 --> 00:17:01,059
What bride deserts her husband on the very day of marriage?

00:17:01,059 --> 00:17:05,509
No, no, Holmes, there's villainy here, and we shall find it.

00:17:05,509 --> 00:17:08,670
Smiling faintly, we shall see.

00:17:08,670 --> 00:17:13,489
Lestrade bustled about the room, imparting a few inconsequential details of his inquiries.

00:17:13,489 --> 00:17:16,309
Omen then took his leave with an air of confidence.

00:17:16,309 --> 00:17:18,739
Holmes watched him go with an amused expression.

00:17:18,739 --> 00:17:23,539
Poor Lestrade! He works with vigour but without vision.

00:17:23,539 --> 00:17:26,969
And you, Holmes, what course shall you pursue?

00:17:26,969 --> 00:17:29,269
The simplest of all.

00:17:29,269 --> 00:17:32,469
I shall insert a small notice in the evening papers,

00:17:32,469 --> 00:17:36,319
couched in terms which our quarry cannot fail to recognise.

00:17:36,319 --> 00:17:42,639
By this means, Watson, I shall bring the lady and her companion to our very door.

00:17:42,639 --> 00:17:44,639
You expect them to come here?

00:17:44,639 --> 00:17:50,880
Where else? When the bird is weary of flight, it will return to the nest of reason.

00:17:50,880 --> 00:17:59,659
He seated himself at the table, drew forth pen and ink, and in a few deft strokes composed an advertisement which, I confess, I found most enigmatic.

00:17:59,660 --> 00:18:04,759
It ran thus. Would the gentleman who accompanied a lady in white satin at Hyde Park yesterday

00:18:04,759 --> 00:18:09,220
kindly communicate with Mr. Poor, Sherlock Holmes, 221 B Baker Street,

00:18:09,220 --> 00:18:13,539
regarding a matter of utmost importance? And you think this will suffice?

00:18:13,539 --> 00:18:18,420
It must, for the lady and her companion cannot long remain hidden.

00:18:18,420 --> 00:18:24,759
Their very secrecy will drive them to seek explanation, and I am the natural medium.

00:18:24,759 --> 00:18:31,230
He laid aside the pen with an air of finality, lit his pipe and leaned back in his chair,

00:18:31,230 --> 00:18:33,630
his eyes gleaming with quiet confidence.

00:18:33,630 --> 00:18:36,759
I, for my part, could not repress his sense of wonder.

00:18:36,759 --> 00:18:38,909
To me, the case seemed zapped in shadows.

00:18:38,909 --> 00:18:41,259
To him, it was as clear as day.

00:18:41,259 --> 00:18:43,079
Thus, the stage was set.

00:18:43,079 --> 00:18:45,720
We awaited only the response to Holmes' stratagem,

00:18:45,720 --> 00:18:50,680
certain that the mystery of the missing bride was drawing swiftly toward a dramatic solution.

00:18:50,680 --> 00:18:55,820
The advertisement, once dispatched to the evening papers, in all breasts,

00:18:55,820 --> 00:18:59,869
thanked, seemed to me, a fray and reed upon which to lean such weighty hopes.

00:18:59,869 --> 00:19:02,570
Yet my companion showed no trace of uncertainty.

00:19:02,570 --> 00:19:03,440
You me!

00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:07,039
He sat calmly smoking, or stretched languidly upon the city,

00:19:07,039 --> 00:19:10,470
his keen gaze wandering now to the ceiling, now to the fire,

00:19:10,470 --> 00:19:15,110
as though he saw the very pattern of truth written upon the smoke and the flames.

00:19:15,110 --> 00:19:19,320
Holmes, forgive me if I appear dull, but I cannot, for the life of me,

00:19:19,319 --> 00:19:21,980
perceive how a mere notice in the standard is

00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:25,639
to draw a vanished bride and her prestigious companion to our door.

00:19:25,639 --> 00:19:29,079
My dear Watson, you resemble the rustic

00:19:29,079 --> 00:19:31,319
who watches the conjurer's performance

00:19:31,319 --> 00:19:34,649
and marvels at the rabbit's appearance,

00:19:34,649 --> 00:19:38,650
but never observes the deft hand that concealed it.

00:19:38,650 --> 00:19:41,839
The advertisement is not the rabbit, but the hat.

00:19:41,839 --> 00:19:46,779
The lady's companion must scan the newspapers with anxious eye,

00:19:46,779 --> 00:19:52,659
for he knows the hue and cry is abroad when he sees that one man.

00:19:52,659 --> 00:19:57,269
Sherlock Holmes does not threaten, but invites communication.

00:19:57,269 --> 00:20:00,379
He will recognize a chance to explain himself.

00:20:00,379 --> 00:20:03,740
You suppose, then, that he is guiltless?

00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:10,079
Not guiltless, perhaps, but not criminal, in the sense Lestrade conceives.

00:20:10,079 --> 00:20:18,439
Love is not larceny, Watson, nor does affection constitute abduction.

00:20:18,439 --> 00:20:40,079
......................

00:20:40,079 --> 00:20:45,199
chronicle of conjectures. At length I retired, yet scarcely had I drifted into slumber when the

00:20:45,199 --> 00:20:49,539
thought of the missing bride, wandering perhaps friendless in the night, awoke me again and again.

00:20:49,539 --> 00:20:50,619
..

00:20:50,619 --> 00:20:54,589
It was about eleven o'clock the next morning when our bell rang with a sharp peal.

00:20:54,589 --> 00:20:59,230
Mrs. Egg Jenga! Hudson entered with her habitual air of patient wonder,

00:20:59,230 --> 00:21:04,299
bearing the guard of a visitor. Holmes glanced at it, and a smile played upon his lips.

00:21:04,299 --> 00:21:08,200
Ah, Watson, the fish has risen to the bait

00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:12,159
Play, compose yourself for an interview of some delicacy

00:21:12,159 --> 00:21:15,000
A moment later our visitor was shown

00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:18,279
In a woman, plainly dressed, her face pale with anxiety

00:21:18,279 --> 00:21:20,299
Her eyes bright with resolution

00:21:20,299 --> 00:21:22,759
She was of middle years, perhaps forty

00:21:22,759 --> 00:21:25,680
Yet there lingered in her features a faded beauty

00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:28,319
And an expression of habitual endurance

00:21:28,319 --> 00:21:31,200
She curtsied slightly, then sank into the chair

00:21:31,200 --> 00:21:33,179
Holmes indicated, so

00:21:33,179 --> 00:21:35,409
Mr. Sherlock Holmes, I presume?

00:21:35,409 --> 00:21:38,599
Sir, I beg you will excuse the liberty of my coming.

00:21:38,599 --> 00:21:39,799
..

00:21:39,799 --> 00:21:42,429
I saw your notice in the paper this morning,

00:21:42,429 --> 00:21:47,820
and I thought it my duty, yes, my duty, to tell you what I know.

00:21:47,820 --> 00:21:49,539
Your name, madam?

00:21:49,539 --> 00:21:51,909
Fowler, Mrs. Flora.

00:21:51,909 --> 00:21:55,000
Fowler, I am, sir, a lady's maid.

00:21:55,000 --> 00:21:57,799
The maid of Miss Hattie Doran, perhaps?

00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:58,859
..

00:21:58,859 --> 00:22:02,740
Ah, yes, sir, her maid, since she landed in this country.

00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:05,269
and it is for her sake I am here.

00:22:05,269 --> 00:22:06,650
For though she has gone,

00:22:06,650 --> 00:22:08,879
I would not have the word think ill of her.

00:22:08,879 --> 00:22:10,940
...

00:22:10,940 --> 00:22:14,640
No one who has read your mistress's character aright

00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:16,710
could think ill of her.

00:22:16,710 --> 00:22:20,199
But pray, proceed, Mrs. Fowler,

00:22:20,199 --> 00:22:22,180
tell us what you observed.

00:22:22,180 --> 00:22:25,119
Well, sir, on the morning of the wedding

00:22:25,119 --> 00:22:27,230
I was with her as she dressed.

00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:29,259
She was pale, fairly pale,

00:22:29,259 --> 00:22:31,210
and trembled as I fastened her gown.

00:22:31,210 --> 00:22:34,550
More than once, she clasped my hand and said,

00:22:34,550 --> 00:22:37,680
Oh, Flora, I wish this day were over.

00:22:37,680 --> 00:22:42,340
I thought it but maidenly nerves, though I confess my heart misgave me.

00:22:42,340 --> 00:22:46,620
Then, at the church, I saw a slip of paper handed to her.

00:22:46,620 --> 00:22:51,430
She turned as white as her veil, and her lips moved as if she prayed.

00:22:51,430 --> 00:22:55,420
After that, sir, she was like a creature walking in a dream.

00:22:55,420 --> 00:22:57,180
And after the ceremony?

00:22:57,180 --> 00:22:59,920
At Lancaster Gate, she whispered to me,

00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:02,889
If anyone should ask for me, Flora, say nothing.

00:23:02,889 --> 00:23:04,589
Remember, say nothing.

00:23:04,589 --> 00:23:06,380
Then she slipped from the room.

00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:07,799
I never saw her again.

00:23:07,799 --> 00:23:09,360
Who's Orel?

00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:12,019
Did she leave by the front door?

00:23:12,019 --> 00:23:13,860
No, sir.

00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:17,220
By the side entrance, as if she would avoid observation.

00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:20,549
And you have heard nothing since?

00:23:20,549 --> 00:23:22,170
Nothing, sir.

00:23:22,170 --> 00:23:23,599
But I know this.

00:23:23,599 --> 00:23:27,289
She loved another before ever she met Lord St. Simon.

00:23:27,289 --> 00:23:31,359
And if that other called her, she would follow him to the world's end.

00:23:31,359 --> 00:23:34,469
You speak of Mr. Francis Morton?

00:23:34,469 --> 00:23:36,460
Star-tiled. You know his name?

00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:37,679
Yes, he it was.

00:23:37,679 --> 00:23:38,799
..

00:23:38,799 --> 00:23:40,049
That is enough.

00:23:40,049 --> 00:23:42,719
You have acted wisely, Mrs. Fowler,

00:23:42,719 --> 00:23:45,480
and you have relieved your conscience.

00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:49,309
You may rest assured your mistress is in safe hands.

00:23:49,309 --> 00:23:51,839
God bless you, sir.

00:23:51,839 --> 00:23:58,360
With a grateful curtsy, the woman withdrew. Holmes watched her departure with a look of quiet satisfaction.

00:23:58,360 --> 00:23:59,380
To Moldau.

00:23:59,380 --> 00:24:06,230
Well, Holmes, your surmise is confirmed. The lady fled willingly to join this molten. Yet, how should we trace them?

00:24:06,230 --> 00:24:10,359
By waiting, Watson. They will trace themselves.

00:24:10,359 --> 00:24:13,549
Had scarcely uttered the words when once more the bell pealed.

00:24:13,549 --> 00:24:19,240
To know, this time a heavy step was heard upon the stair, and Mrs. Hudson announced, Mr. Francis Moulton.

00:24:19,240 --> 00:24:27,809
Our visitor was a man of strong build, bronzed by sun and wind, with frank, earnest eyes and the carriage of one accustomed to command.

00:24:27,809 --> 00:24:32,920
He entered hastily, as though impatience drove him, and addressed Holmes without preamble.

00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:37,789
Mr. Holmes, I have read your notice. You can save me from a cruel misunderstanding.

00:24:37,789 --> 00:24:40,849
My wife is with me, sir, my lawful wife.

00:24:40,849 --> 00:24:42,240
Your wife? But...

00:24:42,240 --> 00:24:53,099
Pay be seated, Mr. Moten. You interest us exceedingly. If you will favor us with your narrative, the truth shall soon be set right.

00:24:53,099 --> 00:25:12,240
....................

00:25:12,240 --> 00:25:14,869
and lay long between life and death.

00:25:14,869 --> 00:25:17,420
News reached Hattie that I had perished.

00:25:17,420 --> 00:25:20,289
She believed herself a widow.

00:25:20,289 --> 00:25:24,659
Were you, in fact, recovered and only later returned?

00:25:24,659 --> 00:25:25,769
Just so.

00:25:25,769 --> 00:25:28,130
When at last I came to England to seek her,

00:25:28,130 --> 00:25:30,990
I found she had been courted by Lord St. Simon.

00:25:30,990 --> 00:25:32,599
Her father urged the match,

00:25:32,599 --> 00:25:36,329
and she, believing herself free, consented.

00:25:36,329 --> 00:25:37,700
I had but one hope,

00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:40,380
to see her before the ceremony and claim my rights.

00:25:40,380 --> 00:25:42,159
But I arrived too late.

00:25:42,159 --> 00:25:57,539
she was already at the church i sent her a note she knew my hand and she came to me as any true wife must extraordinary and where is she now at lodgings not far from here trembling lest the world brand her faithless

00:25:57,539 --> 00:26:02,300
I would shoo her from scandal, sir, but I cannot bear that she be slain as a runaway bride,

00:26:02,300 --> 00:26:04,420
when in truth she but returned to her husband.

00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:05,619
..

00:26:05,619 --> 00:26:08,559
You have done rightly to come to me, Mr. Modin.

00:26:08,559 --> 00:26:15,019
The truth must be told, though gently, for Lord St. Simon's pride is involved.

00:26:15,019 --> 00:26:16,099
..

00:26:16,099 --> 00:26:20,739
I have no wish to wound him, but my hattie is mine, and no man shall part us.

00:26:20,739 --> 00:26:24,180
His voice rang with a passion that left no doubt of his sincerity.

00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:27,519
Holmes regarded him thoughtfully for a moment, then rose with decision,

00:26:27,519 --> 00:26:31,559
Bring your wife here at once, Mr. Moulton.

00:26:31,559 --> 00:26:35,190
It is better that all parties meet beneath my roof,

00:26:35,190 --> 00:26:40,019
where the explanation may be made without unseemly publicity.

00:26:40,019 --> 00:26:42,589
I shall fetch her instantly.

00:26:42,589 --> 00:26:45,549
He hurried from the room.

00:26:45,549 --> 00:26:47,500
I turned to Holmes in amazement.

00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:49,269
Holmes, this is astounding.

00:26:49,269 --> 00:26:51,480
Who would have dreamed of such a solution?

00:26:51,480 --> 00:26:56,000
Anyone who reasoned from the facts, my dear Watson.

00:26:56,000 --> 00:27:00,259
But to conceal a prior marriage, surely the lady acted indiscreetly?

00:27:00,259 --> 00:27:01,279
..

00:27:01,279 --> 00:27:02,429
Indiscreet, perhaps.

00:27:02,429 --> 00:27:08,590
But she believed herself free, and her error was born of grief, not guile.

00:27:08,590 --> 00:27:10,539
We had but a short time to wait.

00:27:10,539 --> 00:27:12,710
In less than half an hour, Boutin returned,

00:27:12,710 --> 00:27:16,710
leading by the hand a young lady whose beauty shone even through her pallor.

00:27:16,710 --> 00:27:20,150
She was tall, graceful, with eyes of deep blue,

00:27:20,150 --> 00:27:22,700
and a proud carriage softened by distress.

00:27:22,700 --> 00:27:25,960
As she entered, she glanced timidly from Holmes to myself.

00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:28,880
then clung more closely to her companion's arm.

00:27:28,880 --> 00:27:31,900
Mr. Holmes, I am Hattie Moulton,

00:27:31,900 --> 00:27:34,889
or Hattie St. Simon, as the world would call me.

00:27:34,889 --> 00:27:37,699
Oh, sir, what must you think of me?

00:27:37,699 --> 00:27:42,950
That you are a lady placed in a position of singular difficulty,

00:27:42,950 --> 00:27:45,819
and that you have borne it with courage.

00:27:45,819 --> 00:27:46,880
..

00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:49,269
But the shame, the scandal!

00:27:49,269 --> 00:27:53,299
I would have spared Lord St. Simon the pain,

00:27:53,299 --> 00:27:56,180
yet how could I forsake my true husband?

00:27:56,180 --> 00:27:57,319
..

00:27:57,319 --> 00:28:00,089
You could not, madam, nor should you.

00:28:00,089 --> 00:28:03,880
The truth once spoken will justify you.

00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:06,940
She sank into a chair, covering her face with her hands,

00:28:06,940 --> 00:28:08,980
while her husband bent tenderly over her.

00:28:08,980 --> 00:28:11,369
I confess, my heart was touched by the sight.

00:28:11,369 --> 00:28:13,069
For all her wealth and beauty,

00:28:13,069 --> 00:28:16,069
she was but a woman torn between duty and affection,

00:28:16,069 --> 00:28:17,899
and affection had conquered.

00:28:17,899 --> 00:28:21,819
Courage, madam, the hour of explanation approaches.

00:28:21,819 --> 00:28:28,119
I have sent for Lord Saint's Simon, and he will soon be here.

00:28:28,119 --> 00:28:31,339
Starting up. Sent for him?

00:28:31,339 --> 00:28:34,579
Oh, sir, I dread that meeting.

00:28:34,579 --> 00:28:38,799
And you? I dread that meeting.

00:28:38,799 --> 00:28:40,339
..

00:28:40,339 --> 00:28:42,940
Yet it must be faced.

00:28:42,940 --> 00:28:46,799
Better under my roof, where calm counsel may prevail,

00:28:46,799 --> 00:28:49,200
than in the glare of society's gossip.

00:28:49,200 --> 00:28:54,720
At this very moment the sound of wheels was heard, and soon after, a knock upon the door.

00:28:54,720 --> 00:28:58,090
Mrs. A. Hudson announced, Lord Robert St. Simon.

00:28:58,090 --> 00:29:00,030
Holmes's glance met mine.

00:29:00,030 --> 00:29:04,360
Steady, Watson. The curtain rises upon our final act.

00:29:04,360 --> 00:29:05,400
..

00:29:05,400 --> 00:29:07,700
Lord Robert St. Lord Robert St.

00:29:07,700 --> 00:29:12,789
Try it is. Simon entered our sitting room with the air of a man who would sooner have been anywhere else,

00:29:12,789 --> 00:29:15,960
yet whose pride compelled him to maintain an unruffled composure.

00:29:15,960 --> 00:29:19,300
His tall figure was effect, his manner studiedly cold,

00:29:19,300 --> 00:29:24,730
though I detected a tremor about the nostrils and a quickness in his glance which betrayed inner agitation.

00:29:24,730 --> 00:29:27,880
Holmes advanced courteously, motioning him to a chair.

00:29:27,880 --> 00:29:31,639
My lord, I thank you for your punctuality.

00:29:31,639 --> 00:29:37,100
Permit me to present to you Mr. Francis Moten and his wife.

00:29:37,100 --> 00:29:38,120
..

00:29:38,120 --> 00:29:40,759
The nobleman's eyes flashed to the couple who rose as he entered.

00:29:40,759 --> 00:29:47,440
For one instant he stood rigid, as though every drop of blood had left his veins.

00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:52,859
Then his lips compressed, and with a slight intonation of the head, he took the seat indicated.

00:29:52,859 --> 00:29:57,289
Mr. Holmes, you promised me the truth. I perceive that it is before me in flesh and blood.

00:29:57,289 --> 00:30:00,500
Rising, trembling Lord St. Simon.

00:30:00,500 --> 00:30:08,289
Oh, sir, forgive me. I never wished to wrong you. I thought, I believed.

00:30:08,289 --> 00:30:10,700
You believed yourself free, madam.

00:30:10,700 --> 00:30:14,269
and therefore you pledged me vows which were not yours to give.

00:30:14,269 --> 00:30:19,619
Willingly, not knowingly, my heart was buried with Frank.

00:30:19,619 --> 00:30:21,869
Or so I thought, or so I thought.

00:30:21,869 --> 00:30:25,670
When he returned, I was bound to him as ever.

00:30:25,670 --> 00:30:28,099
Oh, believe me, I suffered.

00:30:28,099 --> 00:30:29,680
..

00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:32,670
Firmly, my lord, fault lies not with her but with fate.

00:30:32,670 --> 00:30:35,619
She deemed me dead, yet I lived.

00:30:35,619 --> 00:30:39,619
Would you have had her deny her husband when once she knew the truth?

00:30:39,619 --> 00:30:45,309
Sir, I have no quarrel with you. The lady was deceived, but not by you. I accept that.

00:30:45,309 --> 00:30:47,949
Yet I cannot disguise the humiliation I endure.

00:30:47,949 --> 00:30:53,159
To be deserted upon my wedding day, to become the jest of society, such wounds cut deep.

00:30:53,159 --> 00:30:58,979
And yet, my lord, you emerge from this affair with honour intact.

00:30:58,979 --> 00:31:03,669
Your pride may be wounded, but your integrity is unblemished.

00:31:03,669 --> 00:31:08,539
It would be known that you were the victim of circumstance, not of corkwetly.

00:31:08,539 --> 00:31:12,539
Indeed, Lord St. Simon, no man could blame you.

00:31:12,539 --> 00:31:18,610
The nobleman's eyes softened slightly as he regarded Hattie, who stood pale and trembling beside her husband.

00:31:18,610 --> 00:31:21,269
Adam, I forgive you, but I cannot forget.

00:31:21,269 --> 00:31:26,859
No, you will, I trust, withdraw from the circle where your brief presence has caused so much disturbance.

00:31:26,859 --> 00:31:30,179
We ask nothing else, my lord.

00:31:30,179 --> 00:31:34,630
Frank and I shall return to America where none can reproach us.

00:31:34,630 --> 00:31:37,059
And we shall bless you for your generosity.

00:31:37,059 --> 00:31:42,000
Coldly, I do not seek your blessing, sir, but I wish you no ill.

00:31:42,000 --> 00:31:44,809
The tension of the scene was broken by Holmes,

00:31:44,809 --> 00:31:49,059
who rose and stood between the parties with the air of a judge pronouncing sentence.

00:31:49,059 --> 00:31:51,500
Let us consider the matter closed.

00:31:51,500 --> 00:31:52,599
..

00:31:52,599 --> 00:31:54,579
The truth is plain.

00:31:54,579 --> 00:32:00,019
The lady exonerated, and your lordship's honour beyond reproach.

00:32:00,019 --> 00:32:05,630
Society may chatter for a week, but it will soon turn to some newer scandal.

00:32:05,630 --> 00:32:09,519
Meanwhile, all hearts may be at rest.

00:32:09,519 --> 00:32:11,180
Oh, with a bitter smile.

00:32:11,180 --> 00:32:12,640
Elementary, no doubt, Mr. Holmes.

00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,040
..

00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:15,289
Precisely, my lord.

00:32:15,289 --> 00:32:16,360
Elementary.

00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:19,960
With a bow that was half courteous, half disdainful,

00:32:19,960 --> 00:32:22,170
Lord St. Simon rose and took his leave.

00:32:22,170 --> 00:32:24,780
We heard his cab rattle away into the London streets.

00:32:24,780 --> 00:32:27,320
For some moments, silence waned in our little room.

00:32:27,320 --> 00:32:29,450
Then Hattie sank weeping upon the sofa,

00:32:29,450 --> 00:32:31,059
her husband's arm about her,

00:32:31,059 --> 00:32:32,960
while Holmes busied himself with his pipe,

00:32:32,960 --> 00:32:36,740
as though the drama he had engineered were no more than a passing trifle.

00:32:36,740 --> 00:32:40,329
Holmes, you bear yourself as though nothing remarkable had occurred,

00:32:40,329 --> 00:32:44,720
yet we have just witnessed one of the most extraordinary scenes in our experience.

00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:50,370
My dear Watson, extraordinary only to the uninitiated.

00:32:50,370 --> 00:32:55,079
To me, it was the inevitable resolution of given premises.

00:32:55,079 --> 00:32:56,100
..

00:32:56,100 --> 00:32:59,319
Still, you must allow me to marvel at the neatness with which it has ended.

00:32:59,319 --> 00:33:03,579
Meatness is the very essence of deduction.

00:33:03,579 --> 00:33:10,139
When the reasoning is correct, the conclusion follows as surey as day from dawn.

00:33:10,139 --> 00:33:14,619
Hoy, turn then to our guests, whose emotion had somewhat abated.

00:33:14,619 --> 00:33:20,720
Mr. and Mrs. Moulton, you may rest assured that no further impediment lies before you.

00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:29,289
I advise you to depart quietly for America as you propose and to resume the life unjustly interrupted.

00:33:29,289 --> 00:33:32,190
Mr. Holmes, how can we thank you?

00:33:32,190 --> 00:33:36,659
By forgetting me, madam, and remembering only each other

00:33:36,659 --> 00:33:41,519
Yet we shall never forget that you saved my wife from dishonour

00:33:41,519 --> 00:33:44,259
I saved her only from misconception

00:33:44,259 --> 00:33:48,599
The truth was her own, and truth is the strongest advocate

00:33:48,599 --> 00:33:53,460
With words of gratitude, they departed, leaving us once more alone

00:33:53,460 --> 00:33:58,839
I sat back, drawing a deep breath, still half incredulous of the swift unfolding of events

00:33:58,839 --> 00:34:03,619
Holmes, you have unraveled this tangled skein with astonishing swiftness

00:34:03,619 --> 00:34:04,919
Yet I cannot but wonder

00:34:04,919 --> 00:34:09,380
At what moment did you first divine the existence of a prior marriage?

00:34:09,380 --> 00:34:12,639
At the church door, Watson, figuratively speaking

00:34:12,639 --> 00:34:18,039
A bride receives a note and becomes agitated to the point of pallor

00:34:18,039 --> 00:34:22,019
What message could so move her at such a moment?

00:34:22,019 --> 00:34:27,759
Only one, that the man she truly loved and believed lost still lived

00:34:27,760 --> 00:34:31,520
From that instant, the path was straight.

00:34:31,520 --> 00:34:35,890
Yet you spoke of possibilities, of abduction, of other causes.

00:34:35,890 --> 00:34:43,310
My dear fellow, one must allow for alternative explanations until the decisive fact is verified.

00:34:43,310 --> 00:34:45,620
But inwardly I was convinced.

00:34:45,620 --> 00:34:49,280
He smiled at my expression, half amused, half reproachful.

00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:55,880
Come, Watson, you must cultivate the faculty of imagination, disciplined imagination.

00:34:55,880 --> 00:35:00,800
Facts are seeds. Imagination is the soil.

00:35:00,800 --> 00:35:07,050
Deduction is the harvest. Without imagination, facts remain barren.

00:35:07,050 --> 00:35:12,440
I see, Holmes. Yet I confess, the soil of my imagination is but poor compared with yours.

00:35:12,440 --> 00:35:13,579
..

00:35:13,579 --> 00:35:17,760
Dryly. It is a matter of cultivation, not fertility.

00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:22,240
For some time, we sat in companionable silence, the fire crackling,

00:35:22,239 --> 00:35:29,019
Cousin, the fall pressing against the window panes, at length, home stirred and drew a fresh sheaf of newspapers toward him.

00:35:29,019 --> 00:35:52,239
........................

00:35:52,239 --> 00:35:55,679
And you, Holmes, what remains for you?

00:35:55,679 --> 00:36:01,639
For me, nothing, save the satisfaction of having read the problem aright.

00:36:01,639 --> 00:36:06,609
And for me, the satisfaction of having witnessed again the triumph of your method.

00:36:06,609 --> 00:36:11,599
He looked at me with a gleam of amusement, then leaned back, smoke curling upward from his pipe.

00:36:11,599 --> 00:36:18,500
You are a good chronicler, Watson, though you persist in regarding my small achievements as prodigies.

00:36:18,500 --> 00:36:24,260
Nope. Remember, the world is full of wonders if only one has the eyes to see them.

00:36:24,260 --> 00:36:48,500
.........................

00:36:48,500 --> 00:36:53,199
Baker Street regained its accustomed quiet, my mind continued to dwell upon the singular scenes

00:36:53,199 --> 00:36:57,559
we had lately witnessed. It was one thing to perceive the logical solution of a puzzle.

00:36:57,559 --> 00:37:03,000
It was another to observe the human hearts which beat so anxiously within that puzzle's fring.

00:37:03,000 --> 00:37:07,899
In the days that followed, I noted with interest the manner in which the affair of Lord St. Seep,

00:37:07,899 --> 00:37:12,659
Simon and the Vanished Bride was received by society. As Holmes predicted, the gossip of

00:37:12,659 --> 00:37:17,760
London fastened upon it with greedy tongues. At the clubs, men chuckled behind their hands.

00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:20,260
At afternoon teas, ladies whispered,

00:37:20,260 --> 00:37:24,100
the newspapers, from the morning post to the most sensational evening sheet,

00:37:24,100 --> 00:37:25,990
printed columns of speculation.

00:37:25,990 --> 00:37:30,470
To word there, a Lord St. Simon, however, bore himself an outward carp.

00:37:30,470 --> 00:37:34,850
A brief statement was issued in his name, couched in terms of dignified restraint.

00:37:34,850 --> 00:37:38,660
Circumstances of a private nature have necessitated the withdrawal of Lady St.

00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:40,460
A simone from public life.

00:37:40,460 --> 00:37:41,880
No further comment will be made.

00:37:41,880 --> 00:37:44,690
Thus he shielded his wounded pride with the armour of silence.

00:37:44,690 --> 00:37:46,780
For this, I confess, I felt admiration.

00:37:46,780 --> 00:37:51,610
There was something almost noble in the restraint with which he accepted his humiliation.

00:37:51,610 --> 00:37:54,780
Of Mr. and Mrs. Morden, I heard soon after.

00:37:54,780 --> 00:37:59,210
They had sailed quietly for America, leaving behind them the clamor of tongues.

00:37:59,210 --> 00:38:02,650
Before their departure, however, a letter was brought to Baker Street,

00:38:02,650 --> 00:38:06,530
which Holmes tossed across to me one evening as we sat by the fire.

00:38:06,530 --> 00:38:09,470
Letter? Read by Watson?

00:38:09,470 --> 00:38:13,360
Dear Mr. Holmes, words cannot tell the gratitude we feel.

00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:19,140
You saved me from dishonour in the eyes of the world and gave me back my husband.

00:38:19,140 --> 00:38:22,670
Be assured that, far from the scenes of my brief misery,

00:38:22,670 --> 00:38:26,860
I shall never forget the friend who stood between me and shame.

00:38:26,860 --> 00:38:33,599
.......

00:38:33,599 --> 00:38:37,099
With deepest thanks, Harry Moten.

00:38:37,099 --> 00:38:38,760
..

00:38:38,760 --> 00:38:41,079
I laid the letter down, deeply moved.

00:38:41,079 --> 00:38:43,860
Holmes, this must bring you satisfaction

00:38:43,860 --> 00:38:46,920
Satisfaction of a kind, Watson

00:38:46,920 --> 00:38:49,619
Though not the sort most men crave

00:38:49,619 --> 00:38:52,630
And what sort do you crave?

00:38:52,630 --> 00:38:56,480
The satisfaction of intellectual clarity

00:38:56,480 --> 00:39:01,340
Observe, this case presented itself as a confusion of appearances

00:39:01,340 --> 00:39:06,079
A nobleman deserted, a bride vanished, rumours of abduction

00:39:06,079 --> 00:39:10,159
Yet beneath lay the simplest of human dramas

00:39:10,159 --> 00:39:17,170
A woman bound by vows, thought broken, returning to the man she truly loved.

00:39:17,170 --> 00:39:22,840
Strip away the ornament, and the skeleton of the fact stands revealed.

00:39:22,840 --> 00:39:27,920
That is the satisfaction, to see clearly where others grope.

00:39:27,920 --> 00:39:29,679
..

00:39:29,679 --> 00:39:34,960
Yet surely, Holmes, you cannot be insensible to the human element, the anguish of the lady,

00:39:34,960 --> 00:39:36,899
the wounded pride of Lord Saint Simon.

00:39:36,899 --> 00:39:38,799
O Gamban Bind Simon!

00:39:38,800 --> 00:39:43,060
After a pause, I am not made of marble, Watson

00:39:43,060 --> 00:39:47,880
Yet the detective must school himself to regard emotion as data

00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,700
Not as distraction

00:39:49,700 --> 00:39:54,500
A tear-stained face is but a sign, like a footprint in the clay

00:39:54,500 --> 00:39:59,320
And yet, my dear fellow, sometimes the heart reads more swiftly than the head

00:39:59,320 --> 00:40:03,420
Which is why, Watson, I keep you by my side

00:40:03,420 --> 00:40:09,360
He smiled, a rare, kindly smile which lit for a moment the austere lines of his face

00:40:09,360 --> 00:40:12,400
I felt a sudden warmth of pride in my companionship

00:40:12,400 --> 00:40:14,860
Humble though my share in his achievements might be

00:40:14,860 --> 00:40:20,300
Several days later, as we sat at breakfast, another notice in the papers caught my eye

00:40:20,300 --> 00:40:24,240
It was an announcement that Lord St. Simon had retired from London for the season

00:40:24,240 --> 00:40:26,119
Seeking seclusion in the Highlands

00:40:26,119 --> 00:40:27,579
Holmes observed my glance

00:40:27,579 --> 00:40:32,240
A wise retreat, London is merciless in its gossip

00:40:32,239 --> 00:40:35,759
In a month his name would scarcely be mentioned.

00:40:35,759 --> 00:40:37,479
And what of his future homes?

00:40:37,479 --> 00:40:38,909
Shall he marry again?

00:40:38,909 --> 00:40:40,099
Dryly.

00:40:40,099 --> 00:40:42,379
Society has a short memory

00:40:42,379 --> 00:40:45,840
and an ancient title is a powerful magnet.

00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:47,689
He will wed again, no doubt,

00:40:47,689 --> 00:40:50,479
though perhaps he will regard American heiresses

00:40:50,479 --> 00:40:52,819
with a trifle more caution.

00:40:52,819 --> 00:40:55,559
We both laughed quietly at this,

00:40:55,559 --> 00:40:57,959
though my mirth was tempered by sympathy for the man

00:40:57,959 --> 00:40:59,559
who had lost more than he had gained.

00:40:59,559 --> 00:41:07,500
The case, however, lingered in my thoughts, not for its social scandal, but for the lessons it bore in the method of my friend.

00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:16,809
I resolved, therefore, to question him more closely, for I felt that each problem we encountered was an opportunity for my own instruction in the art of reasoning.

00:41:16,809 --> 00:41:23,970
Holmes, you spoke of the matter as elementary, yet I, who followed every step with anxious eyes, found it anything but simple.

00:41:23,970 --> 00:41:26,779
Will you not explain to me more fully the course of your deductions?

00:41:26,780 --> 00:41:34,780
With pleasure, my dear Watson. Consider first the fact of the note at the church. To the superficial

00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:42,300
mind it is an isolated curiosity. To the analytic mind it is the hinge upon which the whole gaze

00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:50,060
turns. The bride, already pledged, receives a message. Instantly her demeanor changes. What

00:41:50,059 --> 00:41:57,680
message could effect such transformation, one which altered her whole conception of a duty.

00:41:57,680 --> 00:42:04,519
That could be nothing less than the announcement of a husband alive, alive. But might it not have

00:42:04,519 --> 00:42:11,699
been some warning, some threat? Possible, but not probable. A threat would produce fear,

00:42:11,699 --> 00:42:14,619
Perhaps an appeal for protection

00:42:14,619 --> 00:42:21,519
Instead we observe determination, concealment and later voluntary flight

00:42:21,519 --> 00:42:24,099
The inference is irresistible

00:42:24,099 --> 00:42:27,130
Then the sighting in Hyde Park?

00:42:27,130 --> 00:42:28,399
Confirmation

00:42:28,399 --> 00:42:32,219
She was seen walking calmly, arm in arm, with a gentleman

00:42:32,219 --> 00:42:34,899
No abduction there, but reunion

00:42:34,899 --> 00:42:37,229
And the maid's testimony?

00:42:37,229 --> 00:42:39,179
Merely the final link

00:42:39,179 --> 00:42:43,920
In truth, I had already reconstructed the story before she spoke a word.

00:42:43,920 --> 00:42:46,050
Holmes, your confidence amazes me.

00:42:46,050 --> 00:42:49,210
I should have hesitated until every piece was in place.

00:42:49,210 --> 00:42:52,880
That is the distinction between us, my dear fellow.

00:42:52,880 --> 00:42:57,089
You require the complete puzzle before you perceive the picture.

00:42:57,089 --> 00:43:01,969
I, by contrast, need but a corner and a hue.

00:43:01,969 --> 00:43:05,179
Yet surely that is genius, not method.

00:43:05,179 --> 00:43:10,329
genius, perhaps, is but method carried to its highest oint.

00:43:10,329 --> 00:43:15,000
Because Hurd's words, uttered with quiet conviction, sank deep into my mind,

00:43:15,000 --> 00:43:20,809
I felt again the gulf between my own laborious reasoning and his swift, intuitive leaps.

00:43:20,809 --> 00:43:23,920
Yet if I could not equal him, I might at least record him,

00:43:23,920 --> 00:43:27,949
and in so doing render some tribute to the singular powers of my friend.

00:43:27,949 --> 00:43:31,119
As the case of the noble bachelor was brought to an end,

00:43:31,119 --> 00:43:34,779
yet before I close my chronicle, I would share one final scene,

00:43:34,780 --> 00:43:38,300
which lingers in my memory with peculiar vividness.

00:43:38,300 --> 00:43:40,910
It was a week later, a grey afternoon,

00:43:40,910 --> 00:43:43,270
the fog drifting once more past our windows,

00:43:43,270 --> 00:43:44,910
Holmes sat at his chemical table,

00:43:44,910 --> 00:43:46,140
bending over some experiment

00:43:46,140 --> 00:43:48,480
while I produced a volume of medical essays.

00:43:48,480 --> 00:43:52,180
Suddenly he looked up, his eyes bright with inward fire.

00:43:52,180 --> 00:43:56,220
Watson, do you know why I cherish such cases as this

00:43:56,220 --> 00:43:58,780
above the most sensational of crimes?

00:43:58,780 --> 00:44:01,019
Because they test your powers of deduction?

00:44:01,019 --> 00:44:05,480
Because they reveal the hidden poetry of life.

00:44:05,480 --> 00:44:09,399
Men think me a machine, a calculating engine.

00:44:09,399 --> 00:44:15,090
Yet beneath the dull crust of facts, there lies the drama of human hearts.

00:44:15,090 --> 00:44:21,399
The nobleman proud but lonely, the girl torn between ambition and love,

00:44:21,399 --> 00:44:25,300
the husband thought dead, returned from the grave.

00:44:25,300 --> 00:44:29,699
All these are but figures in a greater tragedy and comedy.

00:44:29,699 --> 00:44:39,569
To discern their secret, to bring light where there is darkness, that is art, Watson, the highest art.

00:44:39,569 --> 00:44:44,710
Then you admit, Holmes, that even the cold logician may feel the throb of romance?

00:44:44,710 --> 00:44:52,219
Smiling faintly, I admit that romance, when properly analysed, is but logic in disguise. How?

00:44:52,219 --> 00:44:58,919
sanctions he bent again to his retorts and i watching him felt that i had dims for an instant

00:44:58,919 --> 00:45:04,500
the hidden depths of that singular nature the keen brain and the lonely heart united in pursuit of

00:45:04,500 --> 00:45:09,719
truth so ended the adventure of the noble bachelor one of many episodes which have revealed to me the

00:45:09,719 --> 00:45:14,919
strange genius of sherlock holmes and the privilege i enjoy in being his companion and chronicler

00:45:14,919 --> 00:45:15,059
.

